div.div: T_LiDARn: Timestamp of the LiDAR topic
T_imagen: Timestamp of the image topic
lidar_latency: The time gap between the actual LiDAR scan start time and the timestamp of the LiDAR topic
delay_msec: The delay between the LiDAR timestamp and the corresponding image timestamp
camera_jitter: Camera timestamps may fluctuate within a range due to camera jitter
